Okay, let's talk a little bit about warming
up your baby's bottle and how you're going

00:04:48.500 --> 00:04:49.772
to want to do that.

00:04:49.772 --> 00:04:51.960
Do not warm bottles in the microwave.

00:04:51.960 --> 00:04:54.960
This can cause unevenness in temperature.

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:59.990
The best thing to do is to take your prepared
bottle of formula out of the fridge one hour

00:04:59.990 --> 00:05:04.110
